open kali linux and open the terminal

Commmand :-

  1. Install GPG :-
                  Sudo apt install gnupg

2. Generate a GPG Key Pair :-
                              gpg --full-generate-key

3. Encrypting a File :-
                         gpg --encrypt --recipient <recipient-email> <filename>
                          Example :- gpg --encrypt --recipient <email-id> <filename>

4. Decrypting a File :-
                        gpg --decrypt <filename.gpg>




 
              
